### 2. **Basic HTML Structure**

#### `index.html`
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Del Genius Ltd. - Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to Del Genius Ltd.</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="about.html">About Us</a></li>
                <li><a href="courses.html">Courses</a></li>
                <li><a href="contact.html">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>Empowering Minds, Shaping Futures</h2>
            <p>At Del Genius Ltd., we offer a variety of educational resources designed to foster learning and growth.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Del Genius Ltd. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
```

#### `about.html`
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Del Genius Ltd.</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>About Del Genius Ltd.</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="about.html">About Us</a></li>
                <li><a href="courses.html">Courses</a></li>
                <li><a href="contact.html">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>We aim to provide high-quality educational resources to students worldwide, helping them achieve their academic goals.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Del Genius Ltd. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
```

#### `courses.html`
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
